    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. Khan,",
        "I am Muaj Momin, an assistant manager in front office department. I am writing in regards to request some time off for our upcoming Eid festival.",
        "Firstly, I have not seen my family since I have joined here in Mumbai branch. I am really looking forward to see my family on this auspicious occasion of Eid, as my family lives in Banglore, and my sister\u2019s wedding is also fixed, which is right after Eid celebrations.",
        "Secondly, I need 10 days time off dated 15th of November to 25th of November, and I would like to resume work from 26th of November. If I get this 10 days off, I will be helpful to take some decisions on wedding arrangements like, booking a venue, arranging decorations and food and beverage services.",
        "Finally, on the work front, I have already spoken to my colleague Mr. Javed Ali, who is another assistant manager, he will be looking after my shifts during my time off. Nevertheless, after coming back from holiday I will have completed my month end report just before the submission date, which is the 30th of November.",
        "Kindly allow me to take a time off, this will suit my purpose. Looking forward to hearing from you.",
        "Yours Sincerely,",
        "Muaj Momin."
